Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:10.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji took advantage of Sakazaki's rampage to sneak into Ichijou's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:10.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎が暴れている隙に\N一条の部屋に忍び込んだカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:14.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが！凶器の制裁\N血のマニキュア！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:14.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But he receives the brutal punishment of a blood manicure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:17.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ！チキショウ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:15.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:17.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:20.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条の野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:19.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:24.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてシャバでの最終日！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:23.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And today is his final day on the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:29.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Very well. I accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう　受けてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:31.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その挑戦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:34.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初で最後の沼との死闘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's first and last battle with the Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:37.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\pos(640,505)}Prelude to the Showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残された時間 あと７時間！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has only seven hours left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てっ 店長…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:38.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:42.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心配するな　恐れることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:42.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Nothing can possibly go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:45.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の沼は\Nちょっとした思いつきやアイデア
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So what if he things he's figured out the Bog?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:49.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな付け焼き刃で\Nどうかなる代物じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.99,0:00:49.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His ego isn't going to get him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:52.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うか？\Nそ… それはそうですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Er, yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:58.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So it's nothing but fifty million in our pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:57.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となりゃ落ちてるじゃないか\N5000万
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:58.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,拾っとこうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:04.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to hold back. Kaiji's finished when he loses this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:01.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臆することはない\Nこの金を失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:04.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがのカイジくんもアウツ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉砕！決定する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:06.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ruined! Completely bust!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:09.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll live the rest of his life in that abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:09.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生涯 あの地獄の住人に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:17.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ…\Nもう拝まずに済むってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:19.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,After that, I'll never have to see his face again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その暑苦しい顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:27.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ いいだろう\Nやってやれ 磁気チェックだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:26.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and check him for magnets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:29.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold still, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:29.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか 動くなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:38.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長 電話です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:36.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:39.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Phone call from Mr. Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:40.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒崎さまから\N黒崎さま？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kurosaki? This early?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:44.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな時間に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:48.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい 一条です\Nすまんな 朝っぱらから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ichijou speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:48.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:50.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:49.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:53.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は老婆心ながら\Nふと気になってな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:55.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've gotten a bit worried about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:57.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日なんだ　今日が最終日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Today's his final day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:01.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The last day Kaiji will ever spend above ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:01.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのカイジという男が\N地上にいられる最後の日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:05.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I seem to recall his time limit ending at four in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確か 今日の午後４時が\Nタイムリミットと記憶しておるが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:08.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴なら来てます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来てる？\Nええ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:09.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, he came?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:10.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And you let him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入れたのか？\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:12.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:16.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ！軽率だな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:13.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're too careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:18.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでしょうか？\N入れはしましたが問題ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:20.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There should be no problem letting him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:24.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼は完全無欠\N究極の最強マシーンです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:24.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog is invincible! It's the ultimate machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:28.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴は必ず負けます！\N愚か者！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll lose for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:27.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That confidence is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:31.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その自信こそが一番危険なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼に固執していた奴が\Nあの台を打つということは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:36.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he's playing the Bog, he has to have something planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:38.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝算があるからだ\N恐らく５割強は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Probably something that gives him better than 50-50 odds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:43.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな！あり得ません\Nそんなことは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:41.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:45.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝算がありかなしか そんなことを\N今ここで話しても仕方ない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:49.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At this point, it doesn't matter whether he has a plan or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:54.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうなった以上 勝つしかない\Nもちろんです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:52.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:03:03.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't think that you can simply lose that 600 million and still keep your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:57.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メンツうんぬんも さることながら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:00.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現在 たまってる６億を超える大金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:04.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けましたと言って\N済まされる額ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:11.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you lose it, I'm going to have to make an example of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:06.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万が一 負けた場合は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:11.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に過酷かつ破滅的な処遇を\N課すしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:12.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな？\N構いません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That won't be a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:17.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか\Nその覚悟があればいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:17.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. As long as you understand exactly what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:21.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てよ 一条　生きるために
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Win, Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you want to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに来る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's first and last challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:46.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 最初で最後の挑戦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:52.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He risks it all on this pivotal moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:53.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全てを懸け\N満を持して迎えたこの時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:57.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is his last chance to stay above ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:57.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが地上での生を懸けた\Nラストチャンス！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが！出るわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:05.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That idiot! The Bog will never pay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの沼が！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:09.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買いかぶりすぎなんだ 黒崎さまは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kurosaki worries too much about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way he's that far beyond me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:12.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴は俺より はるかに格下！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パッキーだ\Nはっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Paqy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず1000万\Nえっ 1000万？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten million.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:23.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジかよ？\Nどうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why's he doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでやるかね？\N出っこねえのになあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It ain't gonna pay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジくん！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:05:00.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんだな 一条　幕を開けるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:03.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's raise the curtain on our first and final duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:04.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺とお前の最初で最後の真剣勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:08.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後戻りなしだ\Nどっちが滅びるにしても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:08.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no turning back. No matter who's destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:12.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ いいから始めろ さっさと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever. Just get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:17.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思い知らせてやる　お前の傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll show you your hubris!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:19.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Your weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:22.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の脆弱！\Nゆえに生まれた この沼の隙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The chink it opened in the Bog's armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:36.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？\N今 入ったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He got one in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ また… また入ったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:48.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:50.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寄ってるじゃないか 今日は！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Today must be a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:53.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こりゃあ ひょっとすると\Nひょっとするぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He just might pull it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっ どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:03.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on!? Aren't the pins set to "C"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釘設定はＣのはずだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろんです　今朝ちゃんと\Nチェックしましたから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:07.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course! I checked them this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:10.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ あれは何だ？\Nきてるじゃないか 何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:10.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then what's going on!? He's getting far too many in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっ それはその… さっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:13.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I haven't the foggiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きた きた きた！\N今日１回目のクルーン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There we go! His first tray today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,惜しかったー\Nでも いけるいける
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:36.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's still doing good, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:44.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうします？念のため\N発動しときますか？例のﾌﾞﾛｯｸを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:44.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do we do? Shall we activate the block to be safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:48.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや このギャラリー注視の中で\Nそれはあまりしたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:48.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No. I don't want to do it when he has that much of an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:52.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even without it, they're suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:52.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでなくても今\N客の不信感が強い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:57.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この間 坂崎を殺す時\Nちょっと やりすぎたからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:56.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We were too obvious when we finished off Sakazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:00.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The block at the second obstacle is especially blatant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:00.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特に第２関門のブロックが\N露骨すぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:05.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今はダメだ　まっ 釘の森と\N第２関門を抜けても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:06.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if he makes it through the pins and the gate, there's still the trays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだクルーンがある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:10.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those are bulletproof. We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:11.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこは鉄壁！何の問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それより 気に入らないのはあれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What I'm more worried about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The pins are set to "C", right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:22.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釘の設定がＣなんだから\N考えられる可能性は１つ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:22.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can only think of one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ああ そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってこい\Nはっ はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bring me it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:32.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… ではお引き取り願うか\N小悪党に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now to take out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？\Nそこまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中止だ　この勝負は中止！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stop! You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええっ？\Nなっ なんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:42.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why, Ichijou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ 一条？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:48.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… 不満かい？\N不満も何も
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:51.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This just isn't right! You're playing dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:51.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メチャクチャじゃねえか！\Nきたねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちの思惑通り\N運んでる時はいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:58.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't get to just stop games when things don't go how you planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:58.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとでも計算外のことが\N起こると中止 取りやめなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you really want your casino to get a reputation for that kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな理不尽を強いるのか\Nこのカジノは？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:05.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい 何を言う\N当カジノは公正だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:05.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Whatever are you saying? We're perfectly fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:09.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が起ころうと打ち出した以上\Nやめるやめないは打ち手の判断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:10.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, the choice to stop or continue is up to the player.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:13.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,納得のいくまで\N勝負していただいて結構
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:13.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're allowed to play until completely satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:13.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら…\Nただし それは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But that's only if they're playing clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:17.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不正のない場合に限る\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If they happen to be cheating...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴト行為が明らかな場合は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:23.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっ ちょっと待て\N何だ そのゴト行為って？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:23.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, what do you mean "cheating?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pachinko machines are just that. Machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:30.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パチンコってのは １も２も３も台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:33.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,台さえ きちんと\N管理していれば安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:35.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,As long as the machine's operating properly, everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題ないと考えがちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:41.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから監視カメラを増やしてまで\N工作 細工を阻止しようとする
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:40.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why we've made sure that no one could modify it. We even added security cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:48.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But there is one method of doing so that no one expects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:46.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが意外なことに 台以外のものに\N工作 細工されるとは誰も思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:52.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意識の外　そういう意味で\Nカイジくんの狙いは悪くない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It was a clever idea, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:58.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just unlucky that you're not the first person who's tried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくんにとって\N不運だったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:58.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつて同じことをやった奴がいた\Nということだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええっ？\Nカイジくんが今やっているゴト
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:03.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're cheating... by replacing the balls with smaller ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:04.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小玉への玉のすり替え
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:09.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ 何言ってんだ？\Nそれしかないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:16.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's obvious. Setting "C" is packed the tightest of all, but you're still slipping balls through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,設定Ｃという厳しい釘なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:15.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バンバンその狭い空間を\Nくぐり抜けて真ん中に寄っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:20.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば通常より玉が小さいと\N考えるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:20.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That means you must be using small balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:27.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know when you slipped into our storage and replaced the Bog balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:24.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくんが いつどうやって\N別のビルにある補充用の沼の玉を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小玉にすり替えたかは不明だが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:32.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ 台に細工するよりは\Nはるかに易しい仕事と言える
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:32.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure it was easier than breaking the Bog would have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけんじゃねえ\N言いがかりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bullshit! You're making that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長\Nいい加減なこと 抜かすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't just lie like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:40.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… 問答無用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no point in complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,調べれば分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:47.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let me show you. The holes in this plate are the size of normal balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:47.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この検査板の穴は 本来の\Nﾊﾟﾁﾝｺの玉と同じ直径になっている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:54.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If your balls fit through this plate, they're small balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし この板の穴を\N玉が抜けるようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:53.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは通常より小さい\N小玉ってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:10:00.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念だが お前の進撃もこれまで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:59.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sadly for you, this is as far as you'll get.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:10.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… 落ちない？\Nバカな… どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:10.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're not falling! Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ 問題ねえじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, they're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セーフだ セーフだ！\N何だ びっくりさせやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:20.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん\Nああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:23.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:24.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ続けさせてもらうぜ 一条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠慮なくな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I can go back to playing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, guys! I don't know what that was about, but here I go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:29.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 変な水が入ったが再開だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:32.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日はきてる\Nマジで見せられるかもしれねえぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I just might show it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:35.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この沼の爆発 大当たりを！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:35.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This Bog's jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！\N見せてくれ 大当たりを！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's see that jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:45.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな… バカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How is this happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:57.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ　いけ　いけ　いけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:11:03.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうなってるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:11.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If they don't fit through the plate, does that mean they're real!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:09.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この検査板を抜けないってことは\N正常ってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の あの玉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや待て　待てよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:17.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, wait! Maybe the plate itself is fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:17.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも この検査板そのものが\N偽物！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:23.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he was in there, he could have replaced the plate too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:20.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,造作もないことだ\Nありかさえ突き止めていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:23.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,検査板をすり替えることなど…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:24.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 店長！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:38.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If it has smaller, then normal balls will sit higher in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:33.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし検査板の穴が\N通常より小さいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 正常な玉は\Nきっちり はまらずに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やや出っ張り気味に浮き上がる！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:46.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお… 正常だ　正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the real thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだ　一体どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why? What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why do they pass the pins? Why do they enter the gate!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:51.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで寄る？なんで入る？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:55.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normal balls should never make it through setting "C!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正常な玉で設定Ｃだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:57.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入るわけがない！\N入るはずがないんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:57.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:57.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:00.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きたきた！\Nまたクルーンにきた！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:58.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He got another one in the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:01.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼を再開して３日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:07.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's been three days since we set the Bog back up. No one could have rigged it so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:08.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,細工どころか\N触られてもいないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:11.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは日課の釘チェックでも\N確認済み
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus, we check the pins daily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おとといは村上 昨日は俺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:15.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The last three days have been Murakami, me, and Murakami again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:17.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今朝は村上がチェックした\N釘に問題はない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It should be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:20.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… 一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:26.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… 村上の奴\Nずいぶんきつく閉めてやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:26.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Man, Murakami, you sure pack them tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:29.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Murakami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,村上\Nは？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今朝はどうだった？\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How was this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:35.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釘だよ 釘の調整\Nどんな感じだった？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:36.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The pins! How did they feel this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… どんな感じも何も…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice anything unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:42.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you tighten or loosen them!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:42.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今朝 昨日に比べ釘と釘の間を\N開けたのか閉めたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:45.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They needed a little loosening, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:45.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ それは… 若干 開けましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…！\Nああ いえ　もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:50.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They were still well within setting "C!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,設定Ｃの範囲内の話でして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:54.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Tight enough to block all but one of 150 or 200, never mind 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:54.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何しろ あのままだと 100に１つの\N通過どころか 150か200…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やられた！それだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He got us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought the same thing yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:13:01.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も昨日 全く同じことをした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:03.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長 どこへ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, boss!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのガキ！逆発想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That punk kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:14.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He had the other idea, and it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:14.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死角を突いてきやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:18.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He didn't mess with the Bog, he thought of something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:19.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼本体の細工を不可能と見限り\N全く別発想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And it ended up being... This!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あろうことか奴は こっち！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:27.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このゲージ棒の玉の方を細工して\N入れ替えやがった！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:26.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He made a bigger gage, and slipped it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:31.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The setting "C" ball is even bigger than the setting "A" one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:31.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに設定Ｃの玉が\N設定Ａの玉よりでかい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:36.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And he made it bigger day by day so we didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく俺たちが気づかないように
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:36.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しずつ大玉に替えていったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:45.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! With that big of a gap he can just shoot them straight through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:43.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッソー こんなので\N調整していたら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃあ ガバガバになる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:47.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが どうやって…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But how'd he pull it off!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:52.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's only one door, and there's always someone nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:49.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,部屋の入り口は１つ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中には常に店の者が誰かはいる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに忍び込めるわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:57.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He couldn't of snuck in. So how!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:59.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら どうやって これを…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:02.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！何だ これは？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コンクリの破片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Concrete dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:20.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長？\N上だ 上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:24.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He came in from above! Go to the sixth floor, and check the room above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６階に行け！この真上の部屋へ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:27.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？\Nこの上は空き部屋だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Search the empty room there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中を調べろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:42.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もない\Nこっちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:42.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you find something!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:52.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何があった？\Nあ… 穴が！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:51.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:56.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's a huge hole right over the office!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:56.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事務室のちょうど上と\N思われる辺りに バカでかい穴が！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:15:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… やはりそうか　分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I knew it. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やられた　釣り堀だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He fished them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釣り堀？\Nそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fished?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:13.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each day since the Bog came back, he's peeked down through that vent,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼を再開してからの この３日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:13.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく奴は この上の部屋から\Nそこの換気口を通じて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,made sure no one was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:17.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作業を確認できるように\Nセットした
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:22.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and fished up the "C" gage with an electromagnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:19.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして多分 電気磁石を垂らして
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｃ設定のゲージ棒を釣り上げ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:27.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He replaces the ball on the end with a bigger one, and returns it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:28.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上で やや大きめの玉に交換し\N再び戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:32.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このすり替えを\N繰り返してたんだ 奴は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's been doing this over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:36.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Think about it! He's been in this room before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:36.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思い出してみろ\Nこの間 奴はこの部屋に入ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時 ゲージ棒の置き場所が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:41.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He must have noticed we keep the gages under the vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:42.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,換気口の真下にあることに\N気づいたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:46.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに俺とお前が１日交代で\N釘のチェックをする
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:46.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And he knows we alternate days checking the pins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:49.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日替わり体制の弊害 不備を\N突いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:50.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That alternation is our ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ…\N考えてみれば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:57.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Neither of us knew why the previous day's setting was so tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは互いに前日の釘の\N閉まり具合が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:58.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうなってるかを知っちゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:03.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,設定Ｃという標識に\Nただ漠然と従っていただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:03.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Knowing it was still setting "C" blinded us to the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:08.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当のことは何も\N見えちゃいなかった　クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:07.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We didn't notice at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… なっ？\N面白いだろ なかなか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:12.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:17.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼なんかに触らずとも\N細工はできるって話さ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:17.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can even break the Bog without ever touching it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自ら触ることはできなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:24.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't need to, when I have these morons doing it for me every morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:24.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,毎日 律儀に調整してくれる\N間抜けがいるじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てっ 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:33.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,発動だ！ブロックを発動する！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:33.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Activate it! Activate the block!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:36.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の目もクソもない！\N潰すんだ 奴を！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:37.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't care who's watching! Bury him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's in the trays again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きた！\Nきたぞ またクルーンに！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:49.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go! Go go go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:49.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！いけ いけ いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:52.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to do this before they activate the block!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:53.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴がブロックを発動する その前に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:57.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決まれ！決まってしまえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's now or never!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお すげえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've never seen someone get two in the trays at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:02.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２個だ ２個！\Nこんなの初めて見たぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きてる きてる！いけ いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:08.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is my chance! The second gate block is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:09.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャンスだ！敵は２番目の関門の\Nブロックを控えている
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きたんだ\Nこの間のおっちゃんの大暴れが！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:12.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The old man's act did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,インチキ！インチキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It cheats! It cheats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:19.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You! You're the part that does it! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諸悪の根源！死ねー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:23.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが生きた！奴に隙を作らせた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It gave me this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上 客に不信感を\N持たれたくないという
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:27.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to win while they're still hesitant to look like they're cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:28.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隙 ゆるみを！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:34.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！今だ！この機に乗じて\Nひねり込む！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Make it in while I still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あー 惜しい！\Nでもまだ１つ残ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:37.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's still got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:40.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:43.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おー！\Nきたきた ２段目ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:43.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There we go! Second tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ いけー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:06.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あー！\N惜しー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも まだまだ！\Nイエー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:07.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's still in the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完了です\Nよし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:20.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're done, fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:24.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカめ　ここまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:27.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This will finish the whole mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:28.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで この大騒ぎも終結 終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:31.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll never hit the jackpot. It's not even worth dreaming about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:31.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大当たりはおろか\N夢さえ見れなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:35.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう届かないんだからな\Nクルーンには！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:35.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll never even make it to the trays.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:44.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不毛だ　不毛に銀玉を\N費やして死ね！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Keep wasting your balls until you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:48.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね！死ね！死ね！死ね！死ね！\N死ぬがいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:48.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Go ahead and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's not making it to the trays anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行かなくなった　クルーンに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この間のオヤジの時と一緒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:58.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing that happened to the old guy! It just suddenly stops working!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある瞬間から\Nまるで行かなくなったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじくんだよ 全部あれが！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's flipping all the balls away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:04.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not this shit again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:05.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひでえ またかよ！\Nきたねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aim right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:08.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右打ちだ！\Nおお そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:11.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この間 右に流してたら行ったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you aim right, you can still bounce them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:18.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The windmill's stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:19.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,風車が止まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:22.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Anything aimed to the right just drops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:22.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右に流れた玉は\Nそのまま落ちるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:29.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The windmill used to spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この間は あの風車が\N適度に回ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:33.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's how it flipped the balls back to the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ玉は\N真ん中に運ばれもした
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:38.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But now it's useless, even if he tries for a decade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のこの風車じゃ あり得ない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10年打っても！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:42.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッフッフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:48.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've closed that off nice and tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,対策済みさ その点は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:48.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから締めたのさ\N急所の風車をギュウギュウにな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,回らぬ風車だ　どうするカイジ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:52.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That windmill isn't going to spin! What will you do, Kaiji!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:19:59.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What will he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:05.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？どうする？\Nどうする カイジ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:03.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What will he do!? What will Kaiji do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:09.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou stands in his way, wielding the killer block!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:09.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ちはだかる一条\N究極の必殺ブロック
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can he break through!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:14.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるのか 突破 勝利への道！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is there a path to victory!?
